  "description": "[Overview]\nShizuku and Akane… two pilots bound by rivalry and friendship battle to save their world from malevolent cosmic forces!\n\nMulti-directional boomerang-style melee attacks, flamethrowers, burst lasers… a huge range of weapons is at your disposal to mix and match as you customise your ship and battle waves of enemies and bosses across a variety of game modes, including Local Co-Op Duo Play Mode and Boost Mode. Tweak the rules, team up for co-op play, or take on high-score challenges!\n\n[Gameplay]\nPilot the super-advanced Revolgear space fighters Pheasant or Dove, and use precise movement, smart weapon choices and combat skills to earn extra lives and maximise your score!\n\nUse the Bit Shoot attack for boomerang-style melee strikes, the burst system for a powerful energy beam, plus heaps of other weapons and loadouts you’ll unlock as you play!\n\n[Features]\n- Seven stages with four difficulty options.\n- Two main game modes with six possible endings.\n- Over 2,000 equipment combinations. Builds can be customised to suit each player’s preferences.\n- Mission Mode with 30 different challenges to test your skills with various weapons and techniques.\n- An unlock shop where you can obtain custom weapons and gear using in-game currency.\n- Diverse stage designs: from menacing mechs to mystical dragons—anything goes!\n- Two main characters with voice acting. Enjoy dialogues that change depending on the situation.\n- Local co-op! In certain modes, an algorithmic AI partner can also join the fight.\n- Includes the bizarre mystery bonus game “God of Cats”!\n- In-game achievements.",
